value: Indon, PNG, New Guinea, New Guinea
Locally in mangroves and forests of New Guinea
Locally distributed in New Guinea as follows: western coast of the Vogelkop, Onin Peninsula to Etna Bay, head of Geelvink Bay, Huon Peninsula, Huon Gulf and the upper Watut River.
